text: Phillip Van Dyke (born June 13, 1984) is an American former actor. He is best known for portraying the goblin Luke in the first two installments of Disney's Halloweentown film series and Arnold in seasons two and three of Nickelodeon's Hey Arnold!. ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from San Francisco Category:Businesspeople from San Francisco Category:American YouTubers
